'''Andrea''' is a woman who got a pap smear at the practice.

==History==
Andrea came to the practice for a pap smear. It was supposed to be performed by Dell, with Naomi observing, but Andrea observed that Dell was cute and said that he was too cute to do her exam. She asked Naomi to take over.
